Class ruclinicscheduler.MedicalRecord

java.lang.Object
ruclinicscheduler.MedicalRecord
public class ruclinicscheduler.MedicalRecord extends Object
This class is to hold the unique patients with total charges. Deletes user appointments from clinic once transferred to medical record.
Author:
Varun Doreswamy
